des:
You can use the Q-Tran LED App to control smart lighting fixtures in your home with your voice. 
Use the Q-Tran LED APP to create scenes and change to them with your voice or set automated changes. 

After connecting Alexa to your Q-Tran LED products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Q-Tran LED" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Q-Tran LED account in our "Q-Tran LED" app;
(3). You need to have some Q-Tran LED devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Q-Tran LED" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Q-Tran LED" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Q-Tran LED" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Q-Tran LED", and you'll be navigated to Q-Tran LED login page;
(9). Input your Q-Tran LED account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
